title: Allman Brothers - 1994-08-30 - NY State Fairgrounds in Syracuse,

notes:
Wavelab 3.3 was originally used to adjust gain to compensate for a
level shift on the source DAT: d1t01 at: 3:55-3:58

The source was on 2 90 minute DAT tapes. Wavelab was used
to crossfade between d2t01 & d2t02, where the source tape
change occurs. No music is missing.

Unfortunately tracks on Disk 2 of tracks 3 - 7 weren't placed in one single track.
